grat_letter:
Dear Love,
From the depth of my heart, I write this letter to express my utmost gratitude to you for the help and support you've given me and the impact you have made in my life. Words are really not enough to express or even quantify how much of a great blessing you have been to me. I thank God for your life and I thank Him for bringing you into my life. You are a true definition of a gift from God. Thank you for believing in me, thank you for loving me, thank you for being a shoulder to cry on, thank you for always being there for me, thank you for helping me pursue my dreams, thank you for supporting me, thank you for 'baby-girl treatment', thank you for the words of wisdom you've spoken into my life, thank you for the prayers you've prayed over me, thank you, thank you for everything. Time and space would not permit me to list them all, but I want you to know I really appreciate you and all you do. My life has been more meaningful, happier, sweeter, more comfortable and generally better with you and I am so grateful this was God's perfect plan for us. 
Thank you from the deepest depth of my heart and I love you.
With lots of love,
Me.
